Exactly.

00:29:25.840 --> 00:29:27.660
If you stop your dad
from riding that sidecar,

00:29:27.670 --> 00:29:28.440
it's the same as saying...

00:29:28.440 --> 00:29:30.440
I said he can't ride, so he can't.

00:29:31.719 --> 00:29:32.519
Alright.

00:29:32.519 --> 00:29:33.719
You really worry me.

00:29:33.719 --> 00:29:34.600
Zhixia,

00:29:36.719 --> 00:29:38.360
about that paternity test,

