So we need to keep it from her.

00:30:50.640 --> 00:30:51.920
Of course I know that.

00:30:53.479 --> 00:30:54.640
You can rest assured.

00:30:55.079 --> 00:30:57.279
This matter
will stay locked inside my stomach.

00:30:57.479 --> 00:30:58.640
I'll never tell your mother.

00:31:00.920 --> 00:31:01.519
Mom.

00:31:01.719 --> 00:31:03.479
Try this strawberry. It's organic.

00:31:05.360 --> 00:31:06.039
I don't want it.

00:31:07.880 --> 00:31:08.999
Meiqi, have some.

00:31:09.480 --> 00:31:11.279
I don't want it either.
It hurts my teeth.

