It's reputable and close to home.

00:35:05.199 --> 00:35:06.559
You don't have to change hospitals.

00:35:07.079 --> 00:35:08.880
But you must change
your attending doctor.

00:35:09.519 --> 00:35:11.320
Mom, I know about that incident.

