The family couldn't accept it,

00:35:15.960 --> 00:35:17.559
so they hired troublemakers
to cause a scene at the hospital.

00:35:17.559 --> 00:35:18.679
When I went for a prenatal check-up,

00:35:18.679 --> 00:35:19.559
I ran into them too.

00:35:19.840 --> 00:35:21.800
It had nothing to do with Dr. Li.

00:35:21.800 --> 00:35:22.679
You know that?

00:35:22.920 --> 00:35:23.840
You know it,

00:35:23.840 --> 00:35:25.639
and you still let him treat you?

00:35:26.079 --> 00:35:27.340
You have to change your doctor.

00:35:29.079 --> 00:35:29.999
I'm not changing.

00:35:31.039 --> 00:35:32.400
My body, my decision.

00:35:32.760 --> 00:35:34.199
Your body, your decision?

00:35:34.559 --> 00:35:35.360
You're carrying

00:35:35.360 --> 00:35:37.119
our Feng family's grandson.

00:35:37.679 --> 00:35:38.199
Mom,

00:35:38.440 --> 00:35:40.320
even if he's your grandson,

00:35:40.679 --> 00:35:41.960
it's still my decision.

00:35:42.079 --> 00:35:43.079
Shen Mingzhu!

00:35:44.199 --> 00:35:45.760
Is that how you talk to me?

00:35:45.790 --> 00:35:46.999
Now that Feng Jianqi's gone,

00:35:46.999 --> 00:35:48.920
you dare to speak to me like this?

00:35:48.920 --> 00:35:50.760
How can you talk to my mom that way?

00:35:50.760 --> 00:35:52.240
I've done everything for you,

00:35:52.240 --> 00:35:54.559
given you the best of everything,
all for your sake.

00:35:54.960 --> 00:35:56.999
You could at least take my advice.

00:35:56.999 --> 00:35:57.840
Right?

00:35:59.360 --> 00:36:00.800
I'm your mother-in-law.

00:36:01.559 --> 00:36:04.079
And the grandmother
of the baby you're carrying.

00:36:07.720 --> 00:36:08.720
Alright, Mom.

00:36:09.479 --> 00:36:10.199
I'm sorry.

00:36:11.400 --> 00:36:13.199
From now on, I'll listen to you.

00:36:13.400 --> 00:36:14.920
Then quit your job.

00:36:15.479 --> 00:36:16.840
I can't quit.

00:36:17.360 --> 00:36:19.079
It's a job I genuinely enjoy.

00:36:19.360 --> 00:36:21.720
My work schedule
is regular and balanced,

00:36:21.920 --> 00:36:23.199
and my boss looks after me.

00:36:23.199 --> 00:36:24.559
It's not tiring at all.

00:36:25.479 --> 00:36:26.559
Keeping busy

00:36:27.079 --> 00:36:28.920
helps me forget a lot of sad things.

00:36:33.039 --> 00:36:33.720
Fine.

00:36:34.679 --> 00:36:35.999
Keep working for now.

00:36:36.599 --> 00:36:38.720
But once you're due, you must quit.

00:36:41.639 --> 00:36:42.800
We'll see when the time comes.

00:36:42.800 --> 00:36:44.039
What do you mean, "we'll see"?

00:36:45.400 --> 00:36:46.360
You have to quit.

00:36:47.320 --> 00:36:48.760
With that little salary you earn,

00:36:48.760 --> 00:36:50.440
it's not even enough to hire a nanny.

00:36:50.599 --> 00:36:52.079
It's not about the salary.

00:36:52.620 --> 00:36:53.999
It's about selling the memberships.

00:36:53.999 --> 00:36:55.850
She'll do whatever it takes
to hit her targets.

00:36:57.280 --> 00:36:57.999
Meiqi.

